OL,4,C'confirmation public inquiry will take
OL,5,Cplace'
OL,7,FA public inquiry is to be held to
OL,8,Fexamine the events which led to Valdo
OL,9,FCalocane stabbing three people to
OL,10,Fdeath in Nottingham in June last year,
OL,11,Fthe families of his victims have said.
OL,13,FCalocane stabbed 19-year-old students
OL,14,FBarnaby Webber and Grace O'Malley-
OL,15,FKumar as they returned from a night
OL,16,Fout in the early hours of June 13 last
OL,17,Fyear, before killing 65-year-old Ian
OL,18,FCoates.
