OL,7,FA statement from their families
OL,8,Frevealed they have had confirmation
OL,9,Fthat a public inquiry will take place,
OL,10,Fafter meeting Health Secretary Wes
OL,11,FStreeting and Attorney General Richard
OL,12,FHermer.
OL,14,FIt said: "Following meetings with the
OL,15,FAttorney General and Health Secretary
OL,16,Fon Tuesday of last week, we are
OL,17,Fpleased to have had confirmation that
OL,18,Fa public inquiry will take place.
