OL,7,FThe families' statement added:
OL,8,F"Progress is slowly being made and we
OL,9,Fwill continue in our fight to ensure
OL,10,Fthere is full organisational and
OL,11,Findividual accountability for the
OL,12,Fhorrific events of 13 June 2023.
OL,14,F"We will also fight to ensure that
OL,15,Fappropriate changes and improvements
OL,16,Fto our systems and laws are made so as
OL,17,Fto ensure that a tragedy of this level
OL,18,Fis prevented from ever happening
OL,19,Fagain."
