OL,7,FCalocane's brother Elias echoed calls
OL,8,Ffrom the victims' relatives for a
OL,9,Fpublic inquiry earlier this week.
OL,11,F"We need some strong recommendations,"
OL,12,Fhe told the BBC's Panorama programme.
OL,14,F"But we can't just say we'll just wait
OL,15,Funtil it finishes how many years down
OL,16,Fthe line and then do something about
OL,17,Fit then. Something needs to happen
OL,18,Fnow."
